{"_path":"/maps/_business/_low-code/budibase","_dir":"_low-code","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Budibase","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"twitter"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://x.com/budibase?utm_campaign=Onboarding&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz--6Ynd76E4FehE07-MjjIZWwvuH2B-KMkxdBPT1TJ5Eh4ci9Wy0q_RZYTIRBsGXz_09u4n_C8GiUe9f8mFjiC6Dj9B4sw&_hsmi=66516363&utm_content=66516363&utm_source=hs_automation","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Twitter"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020 年那会儿 Budibase 从 SlaskHQ 迁移到 Discord，发布了他的第一条推文，尽管点赞数量只有寥寥三个。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031913704.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"推崇 Sarah Drasner 的空盒子概念，即“也许我们可以从一个空盒子开始，这个盒子只包含正在解决的问题的核心用例或问题”，而不是看到周围完整的网站或应用而感到自卑。Budibase 认为它是一个空盒子，为用户抽象了构建 Web 应用的复杂性。PRay 也是如此，并且应当在多用户交互上大有改进。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Joe Johnston（应该是 budibase 成员）在 2020 年发表了 What is custom software development in 2025，讨论了“定制化软件开发”需求的广阔场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定制软件开发是指为特定问题、用户或人群设计、开发、部署、维护和提供软件支持的过程。理解定制软件开发的关键在于认识到正在开发的解决方案是为单一、特定的目的/问题量身定制的——通常无法通过现有的解决方案来解决。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SaaS 软件（COTS 商业现货软件）单价比定制低，但远没有定制乃至自建来得灵活。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“when COTS software did not solve the problem for SMEs, tools like Excel and Access were drafted in and a solution glued together”，Excel 作为从业者的信息交换工具，类似 Python、Lua 在游戏引擎中的胶水作用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今天正好是 2025 年 1 月，我认为 budibase 对软件开发的认识很有前瞻性。其观点也符合我的两点认识：第一，软件开发应该面向更广阔的 C 端，在知识爆炸并有势形成超级个体的时代，代码技能（实际上是指通过人机界面制定规则并实现需求）是全民必备的技能；第二，新时代的消费包含了新时代的创造，消费时间不仅仅通过娱乐，也可以包含创造性的方式，如同我的世界、乐高等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文章引用了 Percolate、Oribi、Monese 三个工具来说明定制软件如何解决问题，但没用过评价不了。实际上这可能只是为了文章的 SEO。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020-10-02 发布了一个暗黑风格的界面，是制作内容的暗黑风格，而不是 budibase 的。其本地的暗黑模式是在 2020-11-06 号发布的（已经过了公测前两周），不过这速度也太快了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有人发推推荐了一些产品，包括 budibase，剩下一些可能值得观摩的："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://x.com/PoryHQ","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PoryHQ"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://x.com/bildrHQ","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"bildrHQ"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://x.com/draftbit","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"draftbit"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有个 Tag 叫做 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#100DaysOfNoCode"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，看着不错。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bubibase 推荐了 Martin McKeveney 的 NoSQL 和 DynamoDB 的演讲。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"展示了一些预制的渐变色（UI 还可以优化）："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031950748.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020-10-22 发布了不推荐生产环境使用的公共测试版本。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在什么是你建 Web App 时最喜欢的工作内容时，没有人投票给“测试”。不过，反向思考，能辅助用户做测试的工具可能也是很有市场的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031954506.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TechCrunch 的一篇 The No-Code Generation is arriving 文章中，根据“In the distant past, there was a proverbial “digital divide” that bifurcated workers into those who knew how to use computers and those who didn’t.”推演了今后数据分析工程在今后可能作为新的“数字鸿沟”出现以及带来的影响。而这正是过去几年（2017~2020）低代码发力的方向，Airtable 和 Retool 这种年轻的公司分别以 26 亿以及 10 亿美元的估值崛起。文章还提到了“而像 Bildr、Shogun、Bubble、Stacker”等公司，但是我没有用过。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://nocodelist.co/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NocodeList"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，收集了 300+ 无代码工具，而他本身就是一个很适合无代码建设的网站。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032006061.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据看起来还不错，两周的公测信息。公测后两周的数据没有前两周好看。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🔻 606 downloads\n🤖 619 apps created\n🚀 246 apps deployed"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在公测第三个月时，bb 积累了 3200+ 用户、2400+ 应用，以及 554 个部署的应用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020-11-09 发布的图表功能，第一版的功能比较简单，但是很有视觉风格："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032011651.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020-12-20 称自己是“open organization”，可以在 Github 上看到他们的项目路线图，甚至是参与讨论。这种事情（类似完成度的产品）在国内就算放到 2025 年也很难想象。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020-12-09 在 budibase，15 分钟就能创造一个 Winamp 风格的界面。也许包括功能？链接打不开了，无法验证。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032144479.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“将 Star 数量视为开源社区的货币”这一信念让 Joe Johnston 开始 budibase 的 Github 星星之旅。在 11~12 月间，其数量从 83 个增长到了接近 500，在图上来看这就是指数级别的增长！在博客中分享了其做法。时间来到次年 2 月，Star 数量超过 2000，两倍超越了他们的去年的既定目标。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Twitter"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"邮件引导指向 Github 并告知路线图、代码都在 Github"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"budibase 制作的项目支持 Github 调用"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更新 Readme"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"而他们新的 Readme 也确实很有吸引力（“Build business apps 50x faster”）："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032149799.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“As companies, we often look outwards for growth, but looking inwards can provide opportunities. Optimizing processes, analyzing data, & equipping staff with the right tools is often an easier win for many companies; this is where low-code platforms will continue to succeed.”，最有意思的配图。包括上文提到的 2025 软件定制需求前瞻一文中的配图，都是相同类型的矢量图，很有意思。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032152157.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2021 年初，关于希望使用哪个平台托管 bb，居然没有 AWS。前两名 Heroku 和 DigitalOcean 几乎占据了 100% 的投票。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032154794.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"还有另一个投票也显示了 Twitter 上用户的数据库偏好，第一名居然是 Google Sheets。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032156394.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"推荐了一个如何启动开源项目并扩大其影响力的网站，里面有一系列文章："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://opensource.guide/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Open Source Guides"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tech Nation 的 Rising Stars 3 奖项包含了 bb。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2021-04-13 招聘 3 名 JavaScript 工程师。基于之前他发过关于 Svelte 的迷因，我猜创始人对 Svelte 依旧比较感兴趣。同月 25 号，bb 赞助了 Svelte Summit。直到次年 1 月，他们才开始招聘产品负责人、JS 工程师、产品教育经历、产品设计和客户成功经理，可见扩张得比较节制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"那么，下一步是什么？我也想问。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032244873.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"百姓网的知识库里面也有很多内部应用，但是年久失修。我管他们叫幽灵应用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032251644.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2021-10-22 发布了新的响应式拖拽，看起来用户体验很好。PRay 马上跟进。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"video","props":{"src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032256999.mp4","controls":true,"width":"100%"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Your browser does not support the video tag."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不过 bb 的界面很总是看起来很“Notion”。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032308303.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2021-11-16 日，“经过两年的开发，我们激动的宣布正式在 product hunt 上进行官方宣传”。而他们的商业化也确实非常成功。2022-10-03 甚至创办了 5000 刀的低代码马拉松。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032310378.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032318431.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这一切可能都归功于低代码的魔法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032320756.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其中有非常长的一段时间，他们的 Twitter 都是围绕推广和新闻展开，没有其他内容的讨论。直到 2022-11 左右。此时，他们拿到了 @SignalFire 领投的 700 万美元融资。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032316070.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"拿到融资后，Belfast 决定扩大团队规模。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032326207.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Joe Johnston 解释了为何要从 nocode 转型 lowcode。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032329318.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2023 年有许多更新，比如键盘操作，ISO 27001 认证等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032336236.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近一年更新了许多教程，这段时间他们对外宣称自己是“表单创建工具”，并且在博客上也两次拿其他表单创建工具做对比。期间放出不少有意思的应用展示，比如 GPT 克隆（2024-03-11）："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032340672.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在商业化上变得更加大胆，比如推出 Paid Only 功能。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032343927.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在最近（2024-11）的 3.0 更新中，他们解释了之后的路线，主要会包含 